{"tid":2001862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗暴之戰】十一前夕管有汽球等物 兩女獲撤控 呼籲抗爭者別放棄","createTime":"2020-05-05T00:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T00:35:22.000Z","uid":51271,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"853435f50e540d22f215157c96dcc2148969556b","tid":2001862,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T00:14:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200504/IWZWHJF2SFYF6CYRIQBFRZBTVI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200504%2FIWZWHJF2SFYF6CYRIQBFRZBTVI%2F&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1n%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=6d929e28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200504%2FIWZWHJF2SFYF6CYRIQBFRZBTVI%2F&h=cfa49de9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200504/IWZWHJF2SFYF6CYRIQBFRZBTVI/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年10月1日中共建國70周年當天，有市民發起在尖沙嘴舉行「黑氣球活動」，號召參加者在星光大道唱歌及刺破汽球，以示不滿。活動前一天，兩名年輕女子被指在屯門舊咖啡灣泳灘攜有58個汽球及打火機等可疑物品，遭控以管有適合作非法用途工具罪。案件今在屯門裁判法院再訊時，控方主動撤控，辯方沒申請發還訟費。任職教學助理的女被告在庭外直斥警方濫捕，浪費納稅人金錢，又呼籲「大家唔好放棄抗爭者，抗爭者都唔好放棄！光復香港，時代革命！」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全文去蘋果度睇</span>"},{"pid":"e1ff52b3a467ece0feea4e92da9c4fa114b2d39f","tid":2001862,"uid":59518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T00:19:25.000Z","msg":"辯方沒申請發還訟費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6344d762c19cd15c2b7c030204ebece66a32cd","tid":2001862,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T00:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b7ccdd14933b56a82b949843be6af5d464d360","tid":2001862,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T00:30:54.000Z